 Eddie Nartey and Late Wife Vida Nartey Ghanaian Movie Producer and Actor, Eddie Nartey has lost his wife, Vida Ohenewaah Nartey today, Monday, January 25, 2021. The sad news was announced by Eddie Nartey himself on Instagram as he writes a sad message, confirming the demise of his wife. He wrote; “I don’t know what to say, I don’t know what to feel. I’m just in constant pain. Rest well my Habibi. God knows Best. I pray for strength!” View this post on Instagram A post shared by E d d i e   N a r t e y (@eddienartey) The couple tied the knot in a traditional wedding ceremony in 2018.